{
  "video_id": "vrU6YJle6Q4",
  "title": "What makes a good teacher great? | Azul Terronez | TEDxSantoDomingo",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Kesmat El Deeb Reviewer: Riaki Poni≈°t"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17924.0,
      "end_time": 20380.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m obsessed with the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21568.0,
      "end_time": 23838.0,
      "text": "\"What makes a good teacher great?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 25228.0,
      "end_time": 28767.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve collected 26,000 responses to this question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 29677.0,
      "end_time": 31517.0,
      "text": "in eight different schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32570.0,
      "end_time": 34318.0,
      "text": "from the poorest schools in Los Angeles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34448.0,
      "end_time": 38806.0,
      "text": "to suburban schools in Texas, to elite private schools abroad."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 39976.0,
      "end_time": 42704.0,
      "text": "And after 24 years of teaching students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 43314.0,
      "end_time": 45465.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m still perplexed by this question."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 46291.0,
      "end_time": 47675.0,
      "text": "Today, I&#39;m going to teach you"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47675.0,
      "end_time": 50334.0,
      "text": "the lessons I learned from those thousands of students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51245.0,
      "end_time": 56266.0,
      "text": "and learn what I found out from them if we just listen to students."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 56646.0,
      "end_time": 58550.0,
      "text": "The thing about it is"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58550.0,
      "end_time": 60725.0,
      "text": "that during my time of asking kids this question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60725.0,
      "end_time": 65341.0,
      "text": "I realized that we don&#39;t ask this question for a particular reason:"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 65719.0,
      "end_time": 68297.0,
      "text": "schools are afraid."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 69146.0,
      "end_time": 72523.0,
      "text": "Based on fear, they don&#39;t really want to know what kids think."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73166.0,
      "end_time": 76432.0,
      "text": "Partially because they don&#39;t think kids will take it serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 76977.0,
      "end_time": 79848.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to share with you one of the most profound quotes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79848.0,
      "end_time": 82211.0,
      "text": "answers to this question that I&#39;ve ever received."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82881.0,
      "end_time": 84521.0,
      "text": "[A great teacher eats apples]"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 84521.0,
      "end_time": 85562.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85712.0,
      "end_time": 88280.0,
      "text": "Now, I know what you&#39;re thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88540.0,
      "end_time": 90551.0,
      "text": "Doesn&#39;t this prove my point?"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92288.0,
      "end_time": 93997.0,
      "text": "\"Great teachers eat apples.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 95770.0,
      "end_time": 98741.0,
      "text": "When I first saw this, I dismissed it as silliness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99949.0,
      "end_time": 102377.0,
      "text": "but it appeared again and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103930.0,
      "end_time": 104103.0,
      "text": "So I thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104103.0,
      "end_time": 107869.0,
      "text": "\"There&#39;s got to be something to this, but what are they trying to tell me?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108759.0,
      "end_time": 112511.0,
      "text": "So one day, I decided I would start eating apples."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113789.0,
      "end_time": 119980.0,
      "text": "I ate them in the morning, at lunch, during class, in the hall."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 121464.0,
      "end_time": 124164.0,
      "text": "Kids began to give me apples."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 125464.0,
      "end_time": 128574.0,
      "text": "The&#39;d see me eating them and say, \"You&#39;re eating an apple!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129715.0,
      "end_time": 130755.0,
      "text": "\"I know!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 131415.0,
      "end_time": 134561.0,
      "text": "They would smile, and I would smile back."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 135771.0,
      "end_time": 138692.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until I understood that kids wanted to see me"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 138693.0,
      "end_time": 141390.0,
      "text": "as somebody who is willing to receive a gift from them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 142900.0,
      "end_time": 145220.0,
      "text": "that the apple was a symbol for our relationship."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 145732.0,
      "end_time": 148140.0,
      "text": "There was goodness in that, and trust."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 149121.0,
      "end_time": 153722.0,
      "text": "But for a long time, I wasn&#39;t listening and I hadn&#39;t understood this."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 155496.0,
      "end_time": 157900.0,
      "text": "[A great teacher is chill]"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 157190.0,
      "end_time": 158839.0,
      "text": "They have their own language."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 160609.0,
      "end_time": 162649.0,
      "text": "When they say, \"A great teacher is chill,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162649.0,
      "end_time": 165226.0,
      "text": "what they really mean is: \"Don&#39;t take it too serious."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 166308.0,
      "end_time": 170219.0,
      "text": "Be calm in all situations. Don&#39;t get overwhelmed.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 171379.0,
      "end_time": 172749.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 173189.0,
      "end_time": 177109.0,
      "text": "They have a way of speaking to us about what they really want to tell us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 177581.0,
      "end_time": 179861.0,
      "text": "but we have to listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 180171.0,
      "end_time": 181172.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 181172.0,
      "end_time": 184829.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m the father of two grown kids."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 184870.0,
      "end_time": 187501.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re out of school now and in college."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 187857.0,
      "end_time": 190563.0,
      "text": "But when they were at home and they were teenagers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 190563.0,
      "end_time": 192728.0,
      "text": "I had to learn a whole new language."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 193410.0,
      "end_time": 196400.0,
      "text": "When they would come home from school, I might ask them:"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 196400.0,
      "end_time": 200761.0,
      "text": "\"How was your day?\" and they would say, \"Fine,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 201863.0,
      "end_time": 205930.0,
      "text": "which usually meant: \"It was not bad. It was pretty good."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 205375.0,
      "end_time": 207162.0,
      "text": "Nothing happened eventful."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 207162.0,
      "end_time": 209322.0,
      "text": "I probably learned something. Maybe I didn&#39;t.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 210320.0,
      "end_time": 215340.0,
      "text": "But if they came home and said, \"Fine,\" what they meant was:"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 215340.0,
      "end_time": 220172.0,
      "text": "\"It wasn&#39;t really great, but don&#39;t ask me, because you wouldn&#39;t understand anyways.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 221722.0,
      "end_time": 224311.0,
      "text": "If I asked them how their day was and they said \"OK,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225399.0,
      "end_time": 229602.0,
      "text": "what they were trying to tell me was: \"It wasn&#39;t good at at all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 229602.0,
      "end_time": 232131.0,
      "text": "and you should probably ask me more questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 232131.0,
      "end_time": 234431.0,
      "text": "but don&#39;t expect me to answer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 234431.0,
      "end_time": 235730.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 235730.0,
      "end_time": 239828.0,
      "text": "Kids have their own language; they have their own way of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 240735.0,
      "end_time": 242674.0,
      "text": "They want us to think like them"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 242674.0,
      "end_time": 245208.0,
      "text": "and understand what&#39;s inside of their head."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 246477.0,
      "end_time": 250326.0,
      "text": "They have so many ways of thinking that things are great."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 250906.0,
      "end_time": 253973.0,
      "text": "They want us to see their world inside of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 254500.0,
      "end_time": 256464.0,
      "text": "But they don&#39;t want us to act like them;"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 256464.0,
      "end_time": 260334.0,
      "text": "they want us to be calm and protect them and keep them safe."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 260754.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262372.0,
      "text": "Kids have a way of communicating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 262372.0,
      "end_time": 265575.0,
      "text": "and adults just haven&#39;t spent the time listening."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 266132.0,
      "end_time": 267485.0,
      "text": "But what if we did?"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 268650.0,
      "end_time": 271150.0,
      "text": "What if we really listen deeply to students?"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 272688.0,
      "end_time": 273988.0,
      "text": "One of the things I noticed"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 273988.0,
      "end_time": 276758.0,
      "text": "after all the years of collecting these responses"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 277181.0,
      "end_time": 279793.0,
      "text": "is that there is patterns that emerge."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 280763.0,
      "end_time": 283702.0,
      "text": "When I asked the question of what makes a good teacher great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 284214.0,
      "end_time": 288725.0,
      "text": "oftentimes I heard, \"A great teacher loves to teach.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 288995.0,
      "end_time": 292404.0,
      "text": "70 percent of the time, the quote or the answer that followed was:"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 292404.0,
      "end_time": 294734.0,
      "text": "\"A great teacher loves to learn.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 295603.0,
      "end_time": 299862.0,
      "text": "The reason this is significant is they don&#39;t see this happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 299984.0,
      "end_time": 303195.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t see teachers learning in front of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 303728.0,
      "end_time": 305432.0,
      "text": "They see them teaching,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 305432.0,
      "end_time": 308244.0,
      "text": "but they wish they would learn along with them."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 308544.0,
      "end_time": 309554.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 309554.0,
      "end_time": 313830.0,
      "text": "Principals hire teachers to be content experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 313345.0,
      "end_time": 317694.0,
      "text": "to have all of the knowledge, not to be learners."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 318285.0,
      "end_time": 320264.0,
      "text": "But what if they did?"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 320274.0,
      "end_time": 324700.0,
      "text": "What if you showed up in the classroom, and the teacher had something prepared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 324700.0,
      "end_time": 326874.0,
      "text": "said, \"I don&#39;t know exactly what we&#39;re going to do today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 326874.0,
      "end_time": 328681.0,
      "text": "but I can&#39;t wait to learn with you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 328701.0,
      "end_time": 330630.0,
      "text": "Or that they saw their teacher struggle"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 330630.0,
      "end_time": 332792.0,
      "text": "through something they didn&#39;t actually know"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 332792.0,
      "end_time": 335436.0,
      "text": "and then eventually discover the answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 336399.0,
      "end_time": 340660.0,
      "text": "Kids want to be inspired by this idea that learning is important."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 340673.0,
      "end_time": 342656.0,
      "text": "But they don&#39;t see it in schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 343126.0,
      "end_time": 345575.0,
      "text": "[A great teacher isn&#39;t a teacher]"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 345576.0,
      "end_time": 348285.0,
      "text": "When I saw this quote: \"A great teacher isn&#39;t a teacher,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 348285.0,
      "end_time": 350700.0,
      "text": "I actually was a little bit offended."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 350701.0,
      "end_time": 353570.0,
      "text": "\"What do you mean?! I&#39;m a teacher!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 353570.0,
      "end_time": 354744.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re like, \"We know.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 356430.0,
      "end_time": 358230.0,
      "text": "What they were trying to tell me is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 358364.0,
      "end_time": 361577.0,
      "text": "a great teacher isn&#39;t in the classroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 362903.0,
      "end_time": 363973.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 364193.0,
      "end_time": 367263.0,
      "text": "Think about a time that you have some enduring understanding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 367263.0,
      "end_time": 369820.0,
      "text": "a time when you learned something"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 369820.0,
      "end_time": 371423.0,
      "text": "that you still remember and you use to this day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 371423.0,
      "end_time": 375464.0,
      "text": "like throwing a baseball or riding a bike."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376264.0,
      "end_time": 378450.0,
      "text": "I remember learning to ride a bike from my mom"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 378450.0,
      "end_time": 380750.0,
      "text": "when I was five years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 380736.0,
      "end_time": 382835.0,
      "text": "She took off the training wheels of my bike,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 383403.0,
      "end_time": 385429.0,
      "text": "she got behind me, and began to push."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 385981.0,
      "end_time": 387719.0,
      "text": "And we ran, and we ran,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 387726.0,
      "end_time": 391133.0,
      "text": "until she finally let go, and I began to ride a bike."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 392720.0,
      "end_time": 395202.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what I did; that&#39;s how I learned to ride a bike."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 395743.0,
      "end_time": 399582.0,
      "text": "I can still ride a bike to this day from that moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 400779.0,
      "end_time": 404360.0,
      "text": "But can you imagine if I tried to learn to bike from my mom in a classroom,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 404399.0,
      "end_time": 405809.0,
      "text": "what it would look like?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 405809.0,
      "end_time": 407437.0,
      "text": "[Copy this Bike riding 101]"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 407437.0,
      "end_time": 409224.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 409324.0,
      "end_time": 413295.0,
      "text": "\"Son, first, you need to learn all the parts of a bike."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 414296.0,
      "end_time": 418850.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s the pedals and the crank, and there&#39;s a chain that turns the wheel."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 418477.0,
      "end_time": 420623.0,
      "text": "You have to have a significant force;"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 420704.0,
      "end_time": 423815.0,
      "text": "once the force has enough momentum, you can keep your balance."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 424907.0,
      "end_time": 426484.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how a bike works."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 427492.0,
      "end_time": 430822.0,
      "text": "I want you to learn all the parts, be able to label them and draw them."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 430822.0,
      "end_time": 433349.0,
      "text": "Then you&#39;re going to learn and write a research paper"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 433349.0,
      "end_time": 434957.0,
      "text": "about the history of bike riding."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 434962.0,
      "end_time": 436361.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 436712.0,
      "end_time": 441220.0,
      "text": "All the important elements, the adventure, the development of bikes."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 441463.0,
      "end_time": 444514.0,
      "text": "And at the end of that, you&#39;re going to take a final examination."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 444845.0,
      "end_time": 448146.0,
      "text": "If you pass and get an A, you can ride a bike."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 448216.0,
      "end_time": 450850.0,
      "text": "(laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 450490.0,
      "end_time": 453160.0,
      "text": "At five years old, I think I would&#39;ve said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 453166.0,
      "end_time": 454836.0,
      "text": "\"Never mind, I&#39;ll just walk.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 454836.0,
      "end_time": 456147.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 456777.0,
      "end_time": 459250.0,
      "text": "This is exactly what we do to children."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459964.0,
      "end_time": 462508.0,
      "text": "We put them in a classroom and tell them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 462518.0,
      "end_time": 465265.0,
      "text": "\"This is what I want you to learn. It&#39;s important. Do it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 465901.0,
      "end_time": 468620.0,
      "text": "And kids know that it&#39;s not true,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 468620.0,
      "end_time": 471520.0,
      "text": "that we don&#39;t really value learning this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 472540.0,
      "end_time": 476360.0,
      "text": "So no wonder they&#39;re disruptive, or bored, or disengaged."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 477288.0,
      "end_time": 481909.0,
      "text": "Kids want us to be teachers that aren&#39;t teachers."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 482551.0,
      "end_time": 485100.0,
      "text": "I want to tell you a story about Yvette."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 485430.0,
      "end_time": 489191.0,
      "text": "\"A great teacher understands that they have a life outside of school.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 489640.0,
      "end_time": 491263.0,
      "text": "They really do."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 491460.0,
      "end_time": 494829.0,
      "text": "They want us to know that their life in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 494829.0,
      "end_time": 498208.0,
      "text": "is way more different than the life outside of school."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 500530.0,
      "end_time": 503432.0,
      "text": "I just thought, \"Well, how hard is your life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 503741.0,
      "end_time": 507950.0,
      "text": "Your job is to do school; my job is to teach.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 508990.0,
      "end_time": 510727.0,
      "text": "Yvette was a tough student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 511502.0,
      "end_time": 515111.0,
      "text": "She was feisty, and she had an infamous reputation."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 515784.0,
      "end_time": 518365.0,
      "text": "She walked around with a jacket to prove it."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 519172.0,
      "end_time": 522798.0,
      "text": "Whenever she walked around, the kids would follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 523244.0,
      "end_time": 525953.0,
      "text": "She would come in and sit in the front row and lean"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 525953.0,
      "end_time": 529174.0,
      "text": "just so that she can have eye contact to intimidate me."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 529596.0,
      "end_time": 532787.0,
      "text": "She would call me \"mister\" and not even use my full name."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 533426.0,
      "end_time": 537156.0,
      "text": "When she&#39;d get up to go to the bathroom, all the girls would follow."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 537827.0,
      "end_time": 541108.0,
      "text": "Eventually, I learnt from Yvette what she needed to learn."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 541398.0,
      "end_time": 544990.0,
      "text": "And I thought I became pretty good at what I was doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 545480.0,
      "end_time": 548417.0,
      "text": "I noticed one day, she stopped turning in her homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 548978.0,
      "end_time": 551996.0,
      "text": "She had become a great leader in the classroom:"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 552272.0,
      "end_time": 555864.0,
      "text": "she turned in her homework, she participated in class;"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 556272.0,
      "end_time": 558100.0,
      "text": "she actually was quite good."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 558100.0,
      "end_time": 560340.0,
      "text": "So when this happened, I was surprised."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 560622.0,
      "end_time": 564567.0,
      "text": "So I went up to her and said, \"Yvette, I&#39;m very disappointed in you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 565492.0,
      "end_time": 568750.0,
      "text": "She said, \"I know mister; I&#39;m sorry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 570542.0,
      "end_time": 572806.0,
      "text": "\"I expect it turned in tomorrow.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 573249.0,
      "end_time": 578350.0,
      "text": "Tomorrow came, and just a few sheets of unfinished work were turned in."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 579631.0,
      "end_time": 583836.0,
      "text": "I also went up to her and said, \"Yvette, this is disappointing.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 586286.0,
      "end_time": 588994.0,
      "text": "She said, \"I normally do my homework in the bathroom"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 588995.0,
      "end_time": 591431.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s the quietest place in my house,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 593223.0,
      "end_time": 597267.0,
      "text": "but this week the electricity was turned off, and it&#39;s dark in there."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 598468.0,
      "end_time": 600170.0,
      "text": "I had a candle, but it burned out."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 601296.0,
      "end_time": 602380.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m sorry.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 603429.0,
      "end_time": 605908.0,
      "text": "She gazed down, not her prideful self."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 606809.0,
      "end_time": 608516.0,
      "text": "I had missed the point."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 608776.0,
      "end_time": 612467.0,
      "text": "I had not listened when she said, \"I&#39;m trying, mister.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 613268.0,
      "end_time": 615695.0,
      "text": "I heard the words, but I didn&#39;t listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616375.0,
      "end_time": 619189.0,
      "text": "Great teachers notice when there&#39;s a struggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 619815.0,
      "end_time": 623920.0,
      "text": "They don&#39;t make assumptions about what kids can and cannot do."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 624914.0,
      "end_time": 629305.0,
      "text": "They wait and watch, and they rescue them when they&#39;re stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 630605.0,
      "end_time": 633692.0,
      "text": "Good teachers hear them, but they don&#39;t listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 635900.0,
      "end_time": 637645.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll never forget Yvette, and I&#39;m grateful"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 637756.0,
      "end_time": 640380.0,
      "text": "because whenever I see an answer of a student like that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 640380.0,
      "end_time": 642925.0,
      "text": "I remember her, and I listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 643950.0,
      "end_time": 645145.0,
      "text": "[A great teacher sings]"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 645145.0,
      "end_time": 649191.0,
      "text": "This was the most perplexing answer I think I ever received."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 651100.0,
      "end_time": 654913.0,
      "text": "It happened every year for ten years; at least one student would put this."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 655700.0,
      "end_time": 657520.0,
      "text": "\"A great teacher sings.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 658841.0,
      "end_time": 660514.0,
      "text": "What are they talking about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 660611.0,
      "end_time": 661889.0,
      "text": "I can&#39;t sing."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 662140.0,
      "end_time": 666389.0,
      "text": "So I started thinking, \"Wait a second. What do they mean?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 666920.0,
      "end_time": 670884.0,
      "text": "It wasn&#39;t until Danny turned it in as one of his responses."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 672527.0,
      "end_time": 674190.0,
      "text": "He was the class clown."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 674740.0,
      "end_time": 677547.0,
      "text": "You know he was the one that when we took the class picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 677547.0,
      "end_time": 679680.0,
      "text": "he put ear fingers behind your head."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 680270.0,
      "end_time": 682298.0,
      "text": "He would make faces at me during lectures"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 682298.0,
      "end_time": 683328.0,
      "text": "so I would laugh."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 683667.0,
      "end_time": 685784.0,
      "text": "Everything was a joke to Danny."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 686266.0,
      "end_time": 688687.0,
      "text": "So, when he turned in his responses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 689401.0,
      "end_time": 692607.0,
      "text": "and they were all serious and actually really good,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 693500.0,
      "end_time": 695568.0,
      "text": "I was surprised when this showed up in the middle."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 696155.0,
      "end_time": 699329.0,
      "text": "But I knew there was something to it; I just didn&#39;t know what."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 700557.0,
      "end_time": 703686.0,
      "text": "So the next day, I put the agenda on the board,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 703986.0,
      "end_time": 707560.0,
      "text": "listing all the activities of the day, the expectations, and the homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 708126.0,
      "end_time": 713326.0,
      "text": "And instead of actually reading them, very seriously, I sang,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 713516.0,
      "end_time": 714712.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 714792.0,
      "end_time": 717875.0,
      "text": "in an operatic style, big as I could."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 718967.0,
      "end_time": 722227.0,
      "text": "The eyes of the students were wide, their mouths dropped."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 722237.0,
      "end_time": 723597.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 725633.0,
      "end_time": 728153.0,
      "text": "But you know what happened at the end of that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 728403.0,
      "end_time": 731265.0,
      "text": "I expected pointing and laughing."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 731982.0,
      "end_time": 735800.0,
      "text": "But the classroom erupted in cheers and applause."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 736504.0,
      "end_time": 738441.0,
      "text": "There was a standing ovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 739254.0,
      "end_time": 740894.0,
      "text": "I could not believe it."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 741284.0,
      "end_time": 744915.0,
      "text": "At the end of class, they walked out, gave me high fives and handshakes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 744917.0,
      "end_time": 746279.0,
      "text": "and here came Danny."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 746599.0,
      "end_time": 750416.0,
      "text": "He walked in, and he leaned in, and patted me on the shoulder, and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 750416.0,
      "end_time": 752474.0,
      "text": "\"I told you a great teacher sings.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 752504.0,
      "end_time": 754976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 755196.0,
      "end_time": 758396.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 762157.0,
      "end_time": 767236.0,
      "text": "Great teachers make themselves humble before their students."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 768378.0,
      "end_time": 769610.0,
      "text": "They take risks."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 771570.0,
      "end_time": 773730.0,
      "text": "They put aside their fear to try."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 774850.0,
      "end_time": 777709.0,
      "text": "They trust that they are going to be supported if they fail."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 778651.0,
      "end_time": 781102.0,
      "text": "But they don&#39;t see this; they see experts, remember?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 781102.0,
      "end_time": 782419.0,
      "text": "Content experts."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 783263.0,
      "end_time": 785230.0,
      "text": "What if we hire teachers"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 785313.0,
      "end_time": 789559.0,
      "text": "not to be deep understanders of content, knowledge keepers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 789562.0,
      "end_time": 792414.0,
      "text": "but deep understanders of students?"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 793201.0,
      "end_time": 795981.0,
      "text": "How our schools would change and transform?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 797420.0,
      "end_time": 802523.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s no wonder students don&#39;t care or that teachers don&#39;t really listen."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 802924.0,
      "end_time": 804914.0,
      "text": "Because they have never been taught."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 805343.0,
      "end_time": 808150.0,
      "text": "But what if we did listen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 809408.0,
      "end_time": 812855.0,
      "text": "You see, we spend three years of a student&#39;s life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 813606.0,
      "end_time": 815264.0,
      "text": "teaching students to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 815924.0,
      "end_time": 819502.0,
      "text": "About 12 years of those students&#39; lives, teaching them to write."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 820406.0,
      "end_time": 823450.0,
      "text": "Maybe if they&#39;re lucky, they get a semester or half a year"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 824367.0,
      "end_time": 826286.0,
      "text": "learning to public speak."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 827148.0,
      "end_time": 832967.0,
      "text": "But they get virtual zero years of formal listening instruction."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 835246.0,
      "end_time": 836365.0,
      "text": "Zero."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 836618.0,
      "end_time": 837368.0,
      "text": "Think about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 837368.0,
      "end_time": 839714.0,
      "text": "When was the last time you were at a dinner party,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 839714.0,
      "end_time": 842874.0,
      "text": "and someone asked a question: \"So what do you do for a living?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 843179.0,
      "end_time": 846150.0,
      "text": "and the response was, \"Oh, I&#39;m a listening teacher."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 846395.0,
      "end_time": 849130.0,
      "text": "I teach advanced listening at the high school events,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 849416.0,
      "end_time": 852701.0,
      "text": "listening communications, or beginning listener for elementary?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 852701.0,
      "end_time": 853981.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t hear this."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 854452.0,
      "end_time": 858411.0,
      "text": "Because we just don&#39;t believe that in schools it&#39;s important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 858651.0,
      "end_time": 859662.0,
      "text": "though in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 859663.0,
      "end_time": 863871.0,
      "text": "listening is one of the number one skills essential for business and life."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 864157.0,
      "end_time": 866229.0,
      "text": "And we just don&#39;t teach it."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 866683.0,
      "end_time": 869222.0,
      "text": "We need to listen to our students."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 870951.0,
      "end_time": 873880.0,
      "text": "In our classrooms are the future."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 875588.0,
      "end_time": 880613.0,
      "text": "The Maya Angelous, the Mother Theresas, the Elon Musks of the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 881174.0,
      "end_time": 882502.0,
      "text": "And can you imagine"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 882911.0,
      "end_time": 889449.0,
      "text": "if we took the time to ask those students, \"What would make a good teacher great?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 890689.0,
      "end_time": 892279.0,
      "text": "and then we actually listened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 892979.0,
      "end_time": 896100.0,
      "text": "we could transform schools and education."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 897910.0,
      "end_time": 898391.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
